{"tid":436070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文］經過呢件事之後唔會再幫人","createTime":"2017-10-14T21:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T07:31:21.000Z","uid":77486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"abdc41c1c8a6f8dec026595abd274b21dca45390","tid":436070,"uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:58:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係9月10號既凌晨4點半肚餓落7仔買野食<br />\n途中見到個2x歲既後生仔拎住張紙同個女人講野<br />\n我無視佢地直接買左個杯麵食<br />\n食完番屋企途中個後生仔仲係到<br />\n仲走黎同我講<br />\n後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思，我今日晏就打波果時個袋比人偷左，銀包電話鎖鑰都係晒入面，我去左警署報案但仲未有消息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你想點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以借啲錢比我搭車去九龍塘，我朋友幫我check左果到有時鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下...點解唔去觀塘近近地又平好多，同埋你唔去你朋友屋企過夜？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好似上左大陸，我都搵佢唔到，依家唔知點算好，我老豆做中港司機，聽日先番屋企所以要出去過一晚夜<br />\n（當時我都冇錢，本來買野食果時都諗住eps拎定錢第二日唔洗再去撳錢，所以得80蚊係身）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁啦，我得80蚊，我幫你google下觀塘邊間平啲啦<br />\n<br />\n最後我比晒身上僅餘既80蚊加上啱啱係7仔買左兩個杯麵，驚佢未食飯分左一個比佢。<br />\n之後影左佢張報案紙同個樣，save低佢同佢自稱老豆既電話就走左<br />\n<br />\n當時我一開頭都驚係騙案，但係又諗凌晨夜晚晚都就黎呃錢既話，呢個騙徒都幾勤力。再加上一個同我差唔多年紀既人，冇人冇物乜都冇晒係幾咁無助，於是我就信左佢<br />\n<br />\n點知....<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母真係騙子黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時窮到仆街戶口得番200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b130ea2171c9607c5326eb93f58488b0453595ac","tid":436070,"uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/055923_2400fe46a89d78b1f2b033514fbfd523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F055923_2400fe46a89d78b1f2b033514fbfd523.jpg&h=d6a22db1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/055924_2400fe46a89d78b1f2b033514fbfd523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F055924_2400fe46a89d78b1f2b033514fbfd523.jpg&h=2357d415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母落地獄比肥婆雞姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135e867dd8a614e5aa7ed9452909794ee97484af","tid":436070,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:01:32.000Z","msg":"係呃鳩你，咁點"},{"pid":"9607bf8db4d5c534d9bec5e2880c79c474ccfe00","tid":436070,"uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:01:44.000Z","msg":"其實我之後都冇諗過拎番果80蚊<br />\n但估唔到我再次見到你係係fb比人post左上黎話你係呃錢黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c061b4ea233e049a2e2a805d9c1dd8510b05e954","tid":436070,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我之後都冇諗過拎番果80蚊<br />\n但估唔到我再次見到你係係fb比人post左上黎話你係呃錢黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n警告你唔好再po"},{"pid":"badf173f2b431b605419d1cc1cebd2e4e22393c8","tid":436070,"uid":77486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呃鳩你，咁點</blockquote><br />\n利用人同情心，咁樣好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c83c04a85e8b21d24b2a6291938171308cf620","tid":436070,"uid":36942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:03:47.000Z","msg":"隔左成個月你點知佢呃你？<br />\n<br />\n好衰呀佢，你好心幫佢，係佢衰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7fc2fe0087d123a02dfed870dd90d6cca0783","tid":436070,"uid":77486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:05:02.000